      <title>大亨阿达尼将合并水泥公司 Sanghi、Penna 与 Ambuja</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/tycoon-adani-to-merge-cement-units-sanghi-penna-with-ambuja</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 精简了对印度基础设施建设至关重要的业务，阿达尼集团 (Adani Group) 将合并 Ambuja Cements Ltd. 旗下的两个部门，以整合其水泥业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/tycoon-adani-to-merge-cement-units-sanghi-penna-with-ambuja</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 14:02:06 GMT</pubDate>
